gin of the\nhigh-pressure clouds from partial or complete condensation of slow massive star\nejecta, which may have important implication for the puzzle of multiple stellar\npopulations in globular clusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Jan 2023 19:01:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Mar 2023 18:25:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-03"}
