ification of the AB protocol and its finite-state machine (FSM) through\nstate space visualizations, motivated by a search for a formal decomposition\nmethod.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Jan 2023 23:58:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 31 Jan 2023 14:42:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-01"}
