ested in two case studies which\nshows that as the penetration rate of CAVs increases, the total travel time of\nall vehicles decreases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Jan 2023 13:22:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-27"}
