and systematic observations along 10 solar\ncycles since 1908, in H$\\alpha$ and CaII K lines. This paper summarizes 130\nyears of observations, instrumental research and technical advances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Jan 2023 13:59:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-27"}
